# Placeholder so the empty `/public/music` directory stays in Git.
# Copy your real music library here on the deploy host:
#
#   cp -r /path/to/your/Music/* /var/www/cyber-groove-globe/public/music/
#
# Then regenerate the catalog:
#
#   cd server && npm run index-music
#
# Expected layout: continent/country/genre/artist/song.mp3
